Page_0: "Horrus,
See to it that damn railing is fixed. It's been broken for 2 days now and a patron today damn near killed himself. If you don't finish it by the end of the week, I'm docking 5 coppers from your wages. And see if you can search the library balcony for a vaguely ring-like object. One of the nobles claims she lost it while trying to get a better view of the books. I'm sure it will make a nice addition to our forthcoming jewelry section.

-Limes"


